Since the 3.2 update I get a System.StackOverflow when I try to get the index of an item inside a list that contains DisplayMode. Using the example code below will throw the error.
Only tested on WindowsGL

```
protected override void LoadContent() //Unrelated, any method will do the same.
{
         spriteBatch = new SpriteBatch(GraphicsDevice); //Unrelated

         List<DisplayMode> TestList = new List<DisplayMode>();
         TestList.Add(GraphicsDevice.DisplayMode);
         int i = TestList.IndexOf(GraphicsDevice.DisplayMode);
}
```
